{"tid":1790181,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"開花安全線6:1","createTime":"2019-12-19T22:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T14:13:58.000Z","uid":61002,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4f66a7b3fa8d56b1369b9025484a8ed005cbcb40","tid":1790181,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T22:52:03.000Z","msg":"第一，呢個只係基本盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且要多過六區(五區大隊+MAR QRF RAIL BOR APT等) <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同步</span></span><br />\n戰略價值唔可以太過兩極<br />\n同建議各大區域保持局部通車，記得紅隧口最強路障<br />\n[url]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QZYtxnQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQZYtxnQ.jpg&h=dbf5e28a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n第二，非攻，除非決定揭杆起義<br />\n<br />\n小隊目標不贅。<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">主線任務目標係攬炒</span></span>，即刻日常生活不能，搵錢不能，交通不能，開鋪不能<br />\n攬炒唔同焦土，唔係自戕勢力，例如poopoo出咗糧都撳唔到錢消費，或者冇車搭去m巾撈<br />\n攬炒必然惹來對家還擊，包括搞黃鋪，包括恐嚇黃金經濟圈，<span style=\"color: red;\">包括隨機斬人</span>，請準備好隨時fight or flight<br />\n<br />\n第三，反圍捕<br />\n逃生路線/safe heaven要周不時探路update情況。<br />\n特別留意狗車動向，一般而言，車比落地object更危險。*警嫂可以輕鬆守長板橋*<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">架空行人系統、商場屋苑、斜坡、樓梯、隧道</span> 等可有效counter狗車，前提係出口未被封鎖<br />\n(開波之後)逃生時，太多人聚集嘅地方唔會安全，即使平民裝，<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">除非唔怕被逗</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不戀戰</span>，popo大量進駐基本上等於(間接)達成主線任，勁過帝吧出征<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">保持流動</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em>不硬食不被咬不投降不遺忘</em></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ec02e57a25c27e1e219ccf2a5079df6d869b905a","tid":1790181,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T23:00:58.000Z","msg":"街坊師 (遊雞)攻略<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554456</a>"